If you don't know how to make it good do not put it on your menu. The gyro cheese burger appearance was great. I wrapped it up to take a bite,  bit it,  chewed up a lil.  But this burger is completely tasteless,  add bacon,  still no flavor. Tried some of they bbq sauce it added a little bit of flavor. But the kind of bbq sauce they have isn't really set for a cheese burger.  That kind of bbq sauce is made for like pulled pork or something else in which isn't a menu selection here though they do have a wide selection. But this kind of sauce didn't even taste good with the fries. That was a waste of 50 cent. I tried their cheese sauce very flavorless. My food did come pretty fast and this place had good customer service.  A bit pricey for flavorless food. If I were back in this area I may give them another try with a different menu item. But for now I can only give them a thumbs down for a first time visit.
